After nearly killing Patrick Yodar, Sullivan's string of good luck and Dogen's decisive blow took out Conneria and granted the gang the Yoni Egg of Yore. After raiding his hovel, finding a strange substance that the gang made Sullivan drink, our heroes headed back towards the White Woman of the Woods to give her the Yoni Egg of Basket. But not before The Jester attempted to make a deal with them. He'd gift them a magical staff that had happy faces and frowny faces, much to evil Stievel's chagrin, and freedom from the woods if they handed him the yoni egg of Baskin. They, in my opinion, confusingly refused his offer, and instead handed the egg to the white woman, who proceeded to do what you do with such a thing. Her magical yeast infection spread throughout the Whippet Woods, which became more normal, with squirrels and birds and little flowers and nice trees, nothing laughing or cackling or being weird and dark crystal-y. The crew stayed the night, morning, and a bit of the afternoon in her conch shell home in the lake before she tossed them out and sent them to take care of the kitsunes once and for all. Arriving at the scene, they saw a massive tent made of terrible multicolored detritus, organic or otherwise, looking like a freaky circus tent, with a massive foxhole underneath. In the tent they saw the massive beast that belonged to the Vegas brothers, Dean and Luca, saw that it was a massive Sasquatchian thing indeed, except its head and face were that of a human clown. They saw him farting and pranking the Vegas brothers who were tied up at the center of the tent. Also, the beloved Kubler elves were shackled and plodding along,
